{"tid":1846904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局工會加開招募日，未join 快join","createTime":"2020-01-27T19:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T19:51:43.000Z","uid":1654,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56a08650478013649eb778de2888a1d893c3233a","tid":1846904,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:13:03.000Z","msg":"from haea tg channel<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［人多就係最大保障 工會申請人數已過10000人!!!!］<br />\n<br />\n因為反應熱烈，本會將會加開會員招募日，幫大家辦入會手續及收費📈<br />\n<br />\n日期：1月28日（二）<br />\n時間：1700-2200<br />\n地點：旺角道7-9號威特商業大廈9樓<br />\n<br />\n罷工第一件事：加入工會做會員🙇🏿&zwj;♂️  以工會名義罷工先算一齊爭取！<br />\n📍記得先填妥網上申請表：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/36LfYF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36LfYF4&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5lKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=c9565b90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/36LfYF4</a><br />\n<br />\n#今朝12:00收到22:00<br />\n#有同事幫成個ward交錢交到要拎利是錢<br />\n#齊上齊落"},{"pid":"25656b2d3e4f54796f89a3fecca1b2b1b8b3cff7","tid":1846904,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:20:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a94158c571e6b17766413bd04207e8dec765627c","tid":1846904,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:21:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80a6f89b7c84bbf547f4b56f2153764afbd156d5","tid":1846904,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bd85c7add8f7fa48055936b4fed1bab43be9cb","tid":1846904,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察招募日都無咁受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}